	(text_box "Strapping pins pulled low to enforce default behaviour.\n\n- GPIO3 Sets JTAG Mode, Enforce Default, not being used.\n- GPIO45 Controls Voltage to Package RAM, enforce 3.3V\n- GPIO46 Low Enters Download Mode if GPIO0 (Boot) is High, Enforce low, controlled by GPIO0."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 20.32 167.64 0)
		(size 36.83 24.13)
